                        <span class="cs-button-text">How much do custom shutters cost?</span>
                    </button>
                    <p class="cs-item-p">Plantation shutters start from $20/sq ft for composite and $25/sq ft for premium wood. Use our <a href="/shutters">cost estimator</a> for a rough estimate, or book a free consultation for an exact quote.</p>
                </li>
                <li class="cs-faq-item">
                    <button class="cs-button">
                        <span class="cs-button-text">How long does installation take?</span>
                    </button>
                    <p class="cs-item-p">From order to installation is typically 2-4 weeks. The actual installation usually takes just a few hours for most homes.</p>
                </li>
                <li class="cs-faq-item">
                    <button class="cs-button">
                        <span class="cs-button-text">Do you offer financing?</span>
                    </button>
                    <p class="cs-item-p">Yes! We offer flexible financing through Wisetack and Klarna. Apply during your consultation for quick approval and affordable monthly payments.</p>
                </li>
            </ul>
            <ul class="cs-faq-group">
                <li class="cs-faq-item">
                    <button class="cs-button">
                        <span class="cs-button-text">What types of window treatments do you offer?</span>
                    </button>
                    <p class="cs-item-p">We specialize in plantation shutters, zebra shades, motorized shades with smart home integration, and exterior shades. Each is custom-measured and professionally installed.</p>
                </li>
                <li class="cs-faq-item">
                    <button class="cs-button">
                        <span class="cs-button-text">Do you handle unusual window shapes?</span>
                    </button>
                    <p class="cs-item-p">Yes! We specialize in custom solutions for arched windows, bay windows, skylights, and other unique architectural features.</p>
                </li>
                <li class="cs-faq-item">
                    <button class="cs-button">
                        <span class="cs-button-text">Can motorized shades connect to smart home systems?</span>
                    </button>
                    <p class="cs-item-p">Yes! Our motorized shades integrate with Alexa, Google Home, and Apple HomeKit. Control with voice, smartphone, or automated schedules.</p>
                </li>
                <li class="cs-faq-item">
                    <button class="cs-button">
                        <span class="cs-button-text">What warranty do you provide?</span>
                    </button>
                    <p class="cs-item-p">All products come with manufacturer warranties, and we stand behind our installation work. Visit our <a href="/warranty">warranty page</a> for full details.</p>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<script>
    const faqItems = Array.from(document.querySelectorAll('.cs-faq-item'));
